formThreeBId.notesToCertificate: We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction cost.The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement, and applying an appropriate basis of preparation; and making estimates that are reasonable in the circumstances.The certificate is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project solely for the purpose to enable comply with requirement of RERA ,and should not be used by any other person or for any other purpose. Accordingly, we do not accept or assume any liability or any duty of care for any other purpose or to any other person to whom this certificate is shown or into whose hands it may come without our prior consent in writing.The RERA Account considered for the purpose of issuing the certificate is as per details mentioned in the certificate, the provision for compliance with maintainence of RERA Account not validiated while issuing the certificate.Land Cost/ Development Cost is taken as per the development agreement executed by the promoter.We have reliedupon information provided by the management for the numbers and areas given for covered and open parking and garages as we are not technical person to certify the same. The same is the case with Carpet Area, Balcony Area and Terrace Area as mentioned in the certi.Land Cost incurred and paid we have not considered amount transferred to capital account as there is no actual cash outflow. Project has received occupancy certificate in june 2021. in case of sale deed we have taken date of sale deed as per the details provided by the management. in some case booking is received in excess of unit consideration but as per promoter that amount is towards the other charges and do not form part of the unit consideration.
